                            <comment id="12790478" author="jukkaz" created="Tue, 15 Dec 2009 00:07:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;In revision I 890573 I made the RTFParser catch the InternalError and throw a nicer TikaException instead. It&apos;s not a final solution to this problem, but at least it makes the symptoms easier to deal with.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
